{"tid":761357,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"應 否 立 法 拎 綜 援 新 移 民 每 月 捐 血 一次 ？","createTime":"2018-07-30T10:21:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-30T15:17:46.000Z","uid":105538,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"779a8de5a1e7951c8b6dd1274b513aba86e96d54","tid":761357,"uid":105538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T10:21:38.000Z","msg":"讚成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1409437-20180729.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1409437-20180729.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=FN1IPIf6A5MM2oCOz3Xkk4S5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=b1eab11e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1409437-20180729.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=ddd76fee\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1409437-20180729.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n政務司司長張建宗在網誌表示，去年全港參與捐血及成功捐血人次，較2016年均下跌約5%。他指出，年輕初次捐血人數，因出生率下降而下跌，呼籲年輕人積極捐血。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗表示，去年全港共有近16萬名捐血人士，當中恆常捐血者超過12萬人，約六成收集到的血液來自16至40歲的人口。因出生率下降，16至25歲的初次捐血人數自2011年開始下跌，由逾35000人跌至去年只有約20000人。<br />\n<br />\n張建宗指，香港人口持續高齡化，用血需求將持續上升。他又指，政府各部門支持捐血行動責無旁貸，本年度公務員編制預計會增加6700個職位，期望這些「新血」可加入捐血者行列。"},{"pid":"17cfe9b510583e99c355f3639a0df649ef98bbbb","tid":761357,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T10:32:46.000Z","msg":"有病唔捐得嗰啲點處置?"},{"pid":"851ecf0316fedaa1be55de53da9e75e058ff41d4","tid":761357,"uid":30142,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"17cfe9b510583e99c355f3639a0df649ef98bbbb","tid":761357,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T10:32:46.000Z","msg":"有病唔捐得嗰啲點處置?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-30T10:34:16.000Z","msg":"大灣區"},{"pid":"cd1e2ee2df7e6225723c8f95ab3eae6279